_sText:
This is a Remake from my Map fy fragles. The Location is a closed Restaurant with a Pub inside. At the Easter Egg position is a AWP. I have put 4 HE Grenades at the Map.It's only 1 Bombsite at the Map. The T Fraction must be blowing the Kitchen up and the CT Fraction must stop this. There are NAV Files into the Pack, so you can play with Bots.
I hope you like it.

Have Fun ;)

Our skillor
